Double check that it's indeed the chrome version they are sending you and
not just a photo of it in their catalog. There is a black version from Blau
that appears to be made for another model that happens to fit the bus as
well. It doesn't have the same type of locking mechanism and although it
will fit it doesn't fit as well.

